Description_lang: Summons a beam of lunar light at your location, increasing your mastery by ${$s2*$mas}%, dealing ${$414613s1*$s1} Arcane damage, and healing you for ${$204069s1*$s1} over $m1 sec.

description_blz.en_US: Summons a beam of lunar light at your location, increasing your mastery by 25%, dealing 448 Arcane damage, and healing you for 4,147 over 8 sec.
description_blz.es_MX: Invoca un haz de luz lunar en tu ubicación que aumenta un 25% tu maestría, inflige 454 p. de daño arcano y te sana 4,320 p. de salud durante 8 s.
description_blz.pt_BR: Evoca um feixe de luz lunar no seu local, aumentando sua maestria em 25%, causando 445 de dano Arcano e curando 4.316 dos seus pontos de vida ao longo de 8 s.
description_blz.de_DE: Beschwört einen Mondlichtstrahl an Eurem Aufenthaltsort, der Eure Meisterschaft um 25% erhöht, 449 Arkanschaden verursacht und Euch im Verlauf von 8 Sek. um 4.292 Gesundheit heilt.
description_blz.en_GB: Summons a beam of lunar light at your location, increasing your mastery by 25%, dealing 446 Arcane damage, and healing you for 4,316 over 8 sec.
description_blz.es_ES: Invoca en tu ubicación un haz de luz lunar que aumenta un 25% tu maestría, inflige 453 p. de daño Arcano y te sana 4324 p. durante 8 s.
description_blz.fr_FR: Invoque à votre emplacement un rayon de lumière lunaire qui augmente votre Maîtrise de 25 %, inflige 456 points de dégâts des arcanes et vous rend 4239 points de vie en 8 s.

description_blz.zh_TW: 在你的位置召喚一道月光，使你的精通提高25%，造成452點秘法傷害，並在8秒內為你治療4,264點生命力。
